      "author": "lavs9",
      "description": "Initial release of Ghostty Terminal for Obsidian.\n\n## What's included\n- Real Ghostty VT parser via ghostty-web WASM (libghostty-vt)\n- Python PTY proxy — no native addons, no electron-rebuild required\n- Auto-reads your Ghostty config (font, colors, cursor, scrollback)\n- Pixel-perfect canvas renderer\n- Multiple terminal panes / splits\n- File Explorer context menu: Open Ghostty Terminal here\n- Shell restart button on exit\n\n## Installation\nDownload `main.js`, `manifest.json`, `styles.css`, and `pty_helper.py` and place them in your vault's `.obsidian/plugins/ghostty-terminal/` folder.",
